<li class='cover' id='bookCover_28507'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/28507.Serpent_Mage"><img alt="Serpent Mage (The Death Gate Cycle, #4)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1327837018l/28507._SY160_.jpg" />
